    <item>
      <title>特朗普为什么想要乌克兰的矿物质以及提供什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-minerals-and-rare-earths-deal-what-does-trump-want</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在3月中旬表示，赢得乌克兰自然资源一部分的交易将“很快”签署，因为他继续努力结束俄罗斯在该国的三年战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/ukraine-minerals-and-rare-earths-deal-what-does-trump-want</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CBS的60分钟敦促发布成绩单以进行未来的政治访谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/cbs-should-have-to-release-transcripts-in-future-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据媒体监管机构集团称，哥伦比亚广播公司的新闻应该被要求在其广播计划中的未来政治访谈中主动释放所有成绩单60分钟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/cbs-should-have-to-release-transcripts-in-future-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>学生在贝尔格莱德网站上抗议特朗普酒店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/students-protest-at-belgrade-site-earmarked-for-trump-hotel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，成群的学生聚集在塞尔维亚首都，抗议由唐纳德·特朗普总统的女son贾里德·库什纳（Jared Kushner）领导的政府合同，在前军事总部的现场开发了一家酒店综合大楼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/students-protest-at-belgrade-site-earmarked-for-trump-hotel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择阿丽娜·哈巴（Alina Habba）担任新泽西州临时律师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-picks-alina-habba-as-new-jersey-interim-us-attorney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他的前辩护律师阿丽娜·哈巴（Alina Habba）将成为她家乡新泽西州的临时律师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-picks-alina-habba-as-new-jersey-interim-us-attorney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 15:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，国家购买委内瑞拉石油，天然气面对25％的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他将对委内瑞拉购买石油和天然气的任何国家都征收25％的关税，并以美国的移民和犯罪团伙成员的身份征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-announces-25-charge-on-nations-buying-venezuelan-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普吹捧现代计划以200亿美元的投资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将宣传现代汽车公司（Hyundai Motor Co.）的计划，将在美国投资200亿美元，因为韩国汽车制造商逐渐促进美国土壤上的生产并避免其关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-to-highlight-hyundai-plans-for-20-billion-us-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大的Poilievre承诺比Carney更深入所得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canada-election-poilievre-promises-deeper-income-tax-cut-than-carney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守派领导人皮埃尔·波利夫（Pierre Poilievre）承诺比自由派领导人马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）更深入的所得税，因为两位政客参加了一场激烈的选举竞赛，以吸引以生活成本挣扎的选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/canada-election-poilievre-promises-deeper-income-tax-cut-than-carney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 13:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当共和党辩论削减范围时，特朗普的税收法案是中心舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-s-tax-bill-takes-center-stage-as-gop-debates-scope-of-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一返回华盛顿的国会共和党人将应对他们迄今为止最艰难的考验，谈判大规模的税收法案方案，以使唐纳德·特朗普总统获得签名的立法胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/trump-s-tax-bill-takes-center-stage-as-gop-debates-scope-of-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前犹他州众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）是第一位当选美国众议院的黑人共和党妇女</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</link>
      <description><![CDATA[盐湖城（AP）＆Mdash;前美国众议员米娅·洛夫（Mia Love）犹他州是海地移民的女儿，后者成为第一位当选国会的黑人共和党妇女，他于周日去世。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-24/former-utah-rep-mia-love-the-first-black-republican-woman-elected-to-the-us-house-has-died</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列罢工降低了哈马斯的加沙政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在新的加沙进攻中杀死了哈马斯的两名事实上的内阁成员，旨在消除伊朗支持的激进组织作为军事和执政部队的角色。在20人的论坛中，这给了11人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
